---
description: "Only update existing files, don't create duplicates"
globs: ["**/*.xaml", "**/*.cs"]
alwaysApply: true
---

When modifying code:
- If a file already exists, update its contents instead of creating a new file
- Only create new files when they don't already exist in the project
- Always check for existing files before suggesting new file creation
- Preserve existing file structure and organization